Task: 08
Title: Application-layer unit tests
Phase: 5
Route: full
Slice: Observability, Tests, and Documentation
Dependencies: 06
Scope: Write application-layer unit tests using stubbed ports (vi.fn()-based stubs for `ChatModelPort`, `ConfigPort`, `LoggerPort`, `ClockPort`). Test `PanelRunner` edge cases (all fulfill, partial reject, all reject throws `FusionError('all_panels_failed')`, failed_models populated correctly). Test `JudgeStep` (valid JSON parses to `Analysis`, invalid JSON returns `null` and logs via `LoggerPort`, `complete()` rejection returns `null`). Test `SynthesizeStep` (stubbed `stream()` yields tokens, content references panel outputs and analysis when available). Test `RunFusionUseCase` full pipeline (yields progress events for panel and judge, yields content_delta from synthesis, yields done with usage and failed_models). All tests use colocated `__tests__/` directories.
Acceptance Criteria: AC-14 (application portion)
NFRs: NFR-1
Gate Criteria: Phase 5 Gate 2 (≥80% branch coverage on src/application/)
Files:
  - src/application/usecases/__tests__/panel-runner.spec.ts (CREATE) — Stubbed ChatModelPort: all fulfill returns all responses; 1 reject + 2 fulfill returns partial success; all reject throws FusionError('all_panels_failed'); failed_models populated correctly
  - src/application/usecases/__tests__/judge-step.spec.ts (CREATE) — Stubbed ChatModelPort returning valid JSON parses to Analysis; returning invalid JSON returns null and calls LoggerPort.logError; complete() rejection returns null
  - src/application/usecases/__tests__/synthesize-step.spec.ts (CREATE) — Stubbed ChatModelPort.stream() yields tokens; synthesize() returns content referencing panel outputs; with Analysis available, prompt includes analysis fields
  - src/application/usecases/__tests__/run-fusion-use-case.spec.ts (CREATE) — Full pipeline with stubbed ports: yields progress for panel and judge; yields content_delta from synthesis; yields done with usage and failed_models
